<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0.5in"><span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial">Ames Laboratory, under a prime contract with the U.S. Department of Energy (DOE) is issuing</span></span><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt"> this Request for Information (RFI) to seek out available sources in the market place and solicit responses from these sources that can provide information and budgetary pricing on products/solutions available that can meet or exceed the listed wants and needs in the specifications in Appendix A for a Learning Management System. Options that could generate additional cost savings and program efficiencies will also be considered. </span></p>
<p style="TEXT-ALIGN: justify; MARGIN-LEFT: 0.5in"><span style="FONT-SIZE: 11pt">The intention is that Ames Laboratory will review the responses and use the information gathered to help develop an RFP that may result in an award that will provide the Ames Laboratory with the best solution based on the criteria of the RFP evaluation.</span></p>

The purpose of this action is to post a presolicitation notice for the subject requirement.&nbsp;
<div><br /></div>
<div>Note: Please refer to the <strong><em>Sources Sought</em></strong> notice posted under this same solicitation number in December, 2018 for additional draft information.&nbsp;</div>
